                        ጥበብ፡ እምቅድመ፡ ዓለም፡ ፈጠረኒ፡ ለተግባሩ፡</hi></q>; (bottom margin, <locus target="#7r"/>) <q xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">ዘከመ፡
                           ወጽአ፡ አማዑቱ፡ ለአርዮስ፡ ዕልው።</hi></q></desc></decoNote>
                     
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7">
